<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<%- include('../partials/head'); %>
	</head>
	<body class="container">
		<header><%- include('../partials/header'); %></header>

		<main>
			<div class="jumbotron">
				<h1 style="text-align: center">Projects</h1>
				<p>Here are a few projects I would like to highlight</p>
				<div
					style="
						display: block;
						text-align: center;
						margin-left: auto;
						margin-right: auto;
						width: 50%;
					"
				>
					<div>
						<h3>Bug Smasher</h3>
						<img src="images/project1.png" style="width: 50%; height: 50%" />
						<p>
							This project consisted of creating a javascript game that involves
							the player to click on the bugs in order to gain points, the more
							points they get the faster the bugs respawn.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Photo Gallery</h3>
						<img src="images/project2.png" style="width: 50%; height: 50%" />
						<p>
							This project shows the ability to create a gallery that would
							automatically change pictures at a certain interval, if you were
							to add pictures to the ftp server you could click the "update"
							button to refresh it.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Custom Form Validation</h3>
						<img src="images/project3.png" style="width: 50%; height: 50%" />
						<p>
							This project shows the ability to duplicate form data into another
							form and also perform a custom validation checker when submitting
							the form.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

		<footer><%- include('../partials/footer'); %></footer>
	</body>
</html>
